phone-sub-saharan-africa-1880-1995 online]\n* Neres, Philip. ''French-speaking West Africa: From Colonial Status to Independence'' (1962) [https://www.questia.com/library/7131716/french-speaking-west-africa-from-colonial-status online]\n* Priestley, Herbert Ingram. ''France overseas: a study of modern imperialism'' (1938) 464pp.\n* Quinn, Frederick. ''The French Overseas Empire'' (2000) [https://www.questia.com/library/1896884/the-french-overseas-empire online]\n* {{cite book |first=Thomas |last=Pakenham |title=The Scramble for Africa, 1876\u20131912 |url=https://archive.org/details/scrambleforafric00pake |url-access=registration |year=1991 |location=New York |publisher=Random House |isbn=978-0-394-51576-2}}.\n* {{cite book |first=Maria |last=Petringa |title=Brazza, A Life for Africa |year=2006 |location=Bloomington, IN |publisher=AuthorHouse |isbn=978-1-4259-1198-0}}.\n* Priestley, Herbert Ingram. (1938) ''France overseas;: A study of modern imperialism'' 463pp; encyclopedic coverage as of late 1930s\n* Roberts, Stephen H. ''History of French Colonial Policy (1870-1925)'' (2 vol 1929) [https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.84402 vol 1 online] also [https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.89866 vol 2 online]; Comprehensive scholarly history\n* {{cite book |first=Spencer |last=Segalla |title=The Moroccan Soul: French Education, Colonial Ethnology, and Muslim Resistance, 1912\u20131956|year=2009 |location=Lincoln|publisher=Nebraska UP|isbn=978-0-8032-1778-2}}.\n* Strother, Christian. \"Waging War on Mosquitoes: Scientific Research and the Formation of Mosquito Brigades in French West Africa, 1899\u20131920.\" ''Journal of the history of medicine and allied sciences'' (2016): jrw005.\n* Thomas, Martin. ''The French Empire Between the Wars: Imperialism, Politics and Society'' (2007) covers 1919\u20131939\n* Thompson, Virginia, and Richard Adloff. ''French West Africa'' (Stanford UP, 1958).\n* Wellington, Donald C. ''French East India companies: A historica